OASISFormat:  0.3
OCamlVersion: >= 3.12
Name:         guizmin
Version:      1.0
Synopsis:     OCaml library for building (bioinformatics) pipelines
Authors:      Philippe Veber
License:      GPL
LicenseFile:  LICENCE
Plugins:      StdFiles (0.3), META (0.3), DevFiles (0.3)
BuildTools:   ocamlbuild
Homepage:     https://github.com/pveber/guizmin

XStdFilesINSTALLFilename: INSTALL
XStdFilesREADME: false
XStdFilesAUTHORS: false

Description:
  This package provides a library and a syntax extension to build bioinformatics pipelines
  . 
  The library is built from a set of components that are both properly typed 
  and dependency-aware. The library offers an access to a couple of standard 
  tools and databases in bioinformatics.


Library guizmin
  Path:               src
  Modules:            GzmUtils, GzmCore, Guizmin
  BuildDepends:       batteries, core, shell, threads
  
Library syntax
  Path:               src/syntax
  Modules:            Pa_guizmin
  FindlibParent:      guizmin
  FindlibName:        syntax
  BuildDepends:       camlp4.lib, camlp4.quotations.o, camlp4.extend
  CompiledObject:     byte
  XMETAType:          syntax
#  XMETARequires:      camlp4, guizmin
  XMETADescription:   Syntax extension for guizmin


